        Lead your powerful combat units on a quest to be the supreme Orion's Belt champion! To participate you just need to 
        register at <a href="http://www.orionsbelt.eu">www.orionsbelt.eu</a> and enter the tournament. The tournament's entry fee is just 2€.
    </p>    
    
